Minishell

This project was created as part of the 42 curriculum by mafzal and mgolasze.

Description

The goal of this project is to recreate Bash behavior in most common cases.

Instructions

1. Open a terminal in the project root.
2. Build the project:
	make
	or
	make re
3. Start minishell:
	./minishell

Useful Make targets

- make: Build the project.
- make re: Rebuild from scratch.
- make clean: Remove object files.
- make fclean: Remove object files and executable.

